// Higher-order
evens := nums.filter(fn(x: int) -> int { return x % 2 == 0; });
doubled := nums.map(fn(x: int) -> int { return x * 2; });
nums.sort(fn(a: int, b: int) -> int { return a - b; });
```

## Maps

```mog
