a + (b * c);        // required
(a + b) == (c + d); // required

// CANNOT CHAIN: non-associative operators (-, /, %, comparisons)
// a - b - c;       // ERROR — use (a - b) - c
```

Operators: `+` `-` `*` `/` `%` `==` `!=` `<` `<=` `>` `>=` `and`/`&&` `or`/`||` `&` `|` `^` `<<` `>>`

