## Plugins

Compile `.mog` files to shared libraries (`.dylib`/`.so`) loadable via `dlopen`:

```mog
// my_plugin.mog
pub fn fibonacci(n: int) -> int {
  if (n <= 1) { return n; }
  return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2);
}

fn internal_helper() -> int {   // not exported (no pub)
  return 42;
}
```

