## Control Flow

```mog
// If/else (also usable as expression)
if (x > 0) {
  println("positive");
} else if (x == 0) {
  println("zero");
} else {
  println("negative");
}

val := if (x > 0) { 1 } else { 0 };

// While
while (x > 0) {
  x = x - 1;
}

// For-in range (exclusive end)
