## Types

| Type | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `int` (i64) | Default integer |
| `float` (f64) | Default float |
| `bool` | `true` / `false` |
| `string` | Heap-allocated, immutable content |
| `i8` `i16` `i32` `i64` | Signed integers |
| `u8` `u16` `u32` `u64` | Unsigned integers |
| `f32` `f64` | Floats |
| `[T]` | Array of T, e.g. `[int]`, `[string]`, `[Point]` |
